<p>Everyone has their headcanons, but what are your stranger ones? The ones that sound very odd and are out there. The ones that aren't common amongst the fandom.</p>
<p>This probably won't sound too odd considering the possible replies, but mine is that there isn't one SCP-001. They say there is one, but it is done to throw people off. SCP-001 is a classification given to the most important/dangerous anomalies the Foundation has, with various fake documents thrown into the mix as a secrecy measure, along with the lie of there only being one.</p>

